      "author": "Mats324",
      "description": "## What's New\n\n- **Card Theme** -- Force light or dark colors on cards (Settings → Card theme)\n- **Image Caching** -- Download card images to your vault for offline access (global or per-note folder, configurable TTL)\n- **Cache Cleanup** -- Browse and delete cached files from a dedicated modal\n\n## Improvements\n\n- **Open Plugin Settings** -- New command with \\Ctrl+Shift+,\\ hotkey\n- **README** -- Updated with new features and settings\n\n## Bug Fixes\n\n- **Thumbnail position** -- Fixed right/left positioning being inverted\n- **minAppVersion compat** -- Replaced getFolderByPath with getAbstractFileByPath for wider version support\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Mats324/cards4links/compare/1.1.0...1.1.3",
